    readTime: '9',
  },
  {
    title: 'Employee Security Training: A 30-Minute Program That Actually Works',
    excerpt: 'Most security training puts people to sleep. Here is a ready-to-use training session — complete with script, real examples, and a follow-up plan — that your team will actually remember.',
