    category: 'Policies & Planning',
    readTime: '8',
  },
  {
    title: 'Essential Security Hardware for Small Business: The 2026 Buying Guide',
    excerpt: 'From YubiKeys to firewalls to backup NAS — exactly what security hardware your small business needs, with specific product recommendations and three budget tiers.',
    href: '/blog/essential-security-hardware/',
    date: '2026-07-14',
